SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id] AS [AccountId], [a0].[Email] AS [AccountOwnerEmail], [a].[Currency] AS [AccountCurrency], [a].[Iban] AS [AccountIban]
FROM [Cards] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Accounts] AS [a] ON [c].[AccountId] = [a].[Id]

SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id] AS [AccountId], [a0].[Email] AS [AccountOwnerEmail], [a].[Currency] AS [AccountCurrency], [a].[Iban] AS [AccountIban]
FROM [Cards] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Accounts] AS [a] ON [c].[AccountId] = [a].[Id]
